    },
    {
      "text": "Ranked as a beta-global city, it is Pakistan's premier industrial and financial centre, with an estimated GDP of over $200 billion (PPP) as of 2021.",
      "source_url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Karachi",
      "source_type": "reference_work",
      "confidence_tier": "reported",
      "fact_id": "fct_002",
      "first_reported": "2026-07-08",
      "last_updated": "2026-07-08",
      "supersedes": null,
      "contradicted_by": null
    },
    {
      "text": "Karachi is a major metropolitan area and is considered Pakistan's most cosmopolitan city, and among the country's most linguistically, ethnically, and religiously diverse regions, as well as one of the country's most progressive and socially liberal cities.",
      "source_url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Karachi",
